  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Objective of this observational multicentric retrospective-prospective study is to describe
      the number and the characteristics of patients with Reverse Transcription Polymerase Chain
      Reaction (RT-PCR) for SARS-CoV2 positivity admitted to Intensive Care Units during the first
      6 months of epidemic.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
